    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu (Hyouton)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 13 (Spell Level 7)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 18</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 29 | <b>Successes:</b> 5</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 17 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 33</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> H, M</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>This technique is identical to Hyourou no Jutsu (p166). The Strength check DC to break the prison is 35, and instead of suffocating the target will fall unconscious after being trapped for 1d4+1 rounds, remaining so until freed.</p>\n\n\n\n",
